where do i enter the business information

To enter your business information for verification, please email our Ad Support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com with the following details:

- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Account Email
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
- Business URL
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. If you have any questions, feel free to ask!

An EHID number is a unique identifier assigned to businesses for verification purposes. It helps in confirming the legitimacy of a business entity. If you're unsure about your EHID number, you might want to check with your business registration documents or contact the relevant authority that issued it.
